Class City

  • java.lang.Object
    • City
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class City
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<City>
    Represents a city that is visitable. A city has a name, a value and a country to which it belongs, by ariving in the city the player gets a bonus, that is subtracted from the city's value.
    Version:
    Computergame 2
    Author:
    Jens Kristian & Thomas Vinther
